157
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:04,840
Brosh-san?

158
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:07,770
What's wrong, exactly?

159
00:09:08,660 --> 00:09:12,610
Lieutenant Ross is... Lieutenant Ross is...

160
00:09:15,110 --> 00:09:18,340
Your hair is as deep black 
as the feathers

161
00:09:18,340 --> 00:09:21,960
