205
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:44,630
You saw Lyra-san?!

206
00:11:44,630 --> 00:11:47,360
Then she must have safely 
gotten away from Dante-san's place!

207
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:49,600
Just a moment, if you please.

208
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:54,280
This Lyra-san—what kind of 
relationship do you two have?

209
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:56,440
Oh, sorry.

210
00:11:55,300 --> 00:11:58,360
