Why are you holding that wrench?

211
00:11:59,110 --> 00:12:00,360
I'm sorry.

212
00:12:08,640 --> 00:12:10,910
The Führer is married,

213
00:12:11,230 --> 00:12:13,000
and he also has children.

214
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:16,570
Above all else, I've seen pictures of him when he was younger.

215
00:12:16,570 --> 00:12:22,220
Homunculi do not take on the form of humans when they are born.

216
00:12:22,820 --> 00:12:25,400
When they are given red stones as a source of nourishment,

217
00:12:25,400 --> 00:12:29,100
they get their own unique powers, as well as their form.

218
00:12:30,540 --> 00:12:32,230
