to get on all right,

231
00:13:12,560 --> 00:13:14,930
and the military is functioning.

232
00:13:14,930 --> 00:13:16,940
We need not concern 
ourselves with them.

233
00:13:18,750 --> 00:13:22,940
Why is it that the homunculi can't use alchemy?

234
00:13:23,930 --> 00:13:26,450
Because they come from 
the other side of the gate.

235
00:13:27,360 --> 00:13:31,450
But let's not talk about that. Tell me all about Trisha,

236
00:13:31,450 --> 00:13:35,120
as well as everything you guys have been struggling through.

237
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:37,460
Dad...

238
00:13:37,460 --> 00:13:40,410
I can tell just by looking 
at your body. You guys—

239
00:13:40,410 --> 00:13:42,510
There isn't anything to talk about.

240
00:13:44,100 --> 00:13:50,410
