252
00:14:32,750 --> 00:14:34,920
That's not what I meant. I...

253
00:14:34,920 --> 00:14:39,470
Your own body was lost in an equivalent exchange.

254
00:14:39,860 --> 00:14:44,000
You must have given up your body as the cost of obtaining something else.

255
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:45,430
Something else?

256
00:14:45,930 --> 00:14:49,170
If you return all of that, 
it will come back.

